{"tid":1511116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Tommy仔】阮民安遭內地網民攻擊 深夜發文「我很窮，我愛人民幣，但我更愛香港」","createTime":"2019-08-27T12:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T01:51:38.000Z","uid":66271,"like":101,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e94a9d2d6d129f6dfb2c69fbb2db80b2cd06cfd5","tid":1511116,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hWN1jOQMiKXnt_se5kMxgA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/ad8814e0-c87b-11e9-bbdf-967f7cf25b9f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhWN1jOQMiKXnt_se5kMxgA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2Fad8814e0-c87b-11e9-bbdf-967f7cf25b9f&h=ce027da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂風波已經持續超過兩個月，E-kids成員阮民安（Tommy）多次被拍到現身示威現場及經常喺個人社交網站發表個人感受，以行動支持「反修例」。繼日前喺社交網站上載同做警察堂哥嘅割蓆對話後，俾網民大讚型過余文樂。噚晚又再喺社交網站以 「我很窮，我愛人民幣，但我更愛香港」為題發表長文。<br />\n<br />\n內容係關於抗爭運動，佢今次好大膽咁為香港發聲，仲話當中有人支持佢，亦有人認為佢係無嘢輸，係想博翻身。Tommy就話會身體力行，繼續發聲，不過突然有內地網民去佢老婆Eva嘅微博，話佢哋支持港獨，攻擊佢哋。於是Tommy就同大家分享佢嘅想法同預計嘅損失，佢哋一家四口透過幫唔同產品做宣傳、時裝騷、電視台嘉賓及上內地綜藝節目賺錢生活。而EVA亦有自家品牌，亦將會喺東京嘅一間知名商場正式發佈，佢哋收入都唔錯。但經過多次高調發聲後，佢可能會失去大陸市場，收入亦會大受影響。不過佢覺得同一班手足比，自己嘅損失並唔算得咩，更相信自己唔一定要靠內地先搵到食。Tommy更話雞蛋與高牆，佢一定喺雞蛋呢邊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e7amTNJAGFxcUVQpOMnHqg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/c6c2d260-c87b-11e9-b36a-8e2609508775\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe7amTNJAGFxcUVQpOMnHqg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2Fc6c2d260-c87b-11e9-b36a-8e2609508775&h=df6aa3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少網民睇完都好支持佢，仲紛紛留言：「而家連周柏豪你都型過佢幾百萬倍。real star !」、「很感動😭男神謝謝你🙇&zwj;♀️you are the best👍」、「Tommy 好真心佩服你，我覺得其他藝人應該以自己為恥 你係榜樣！！」、「支持你👍🏽係錢同良知既天秤上，做出了好多人（特別係公眾人物）都好難做既選擇！大家都要堅持下去✊」、「多謝你，不為五斗米折腰，你品牌推出時，我哋會幫襯，幫你宣傳，自己香港自己救，齊上齊落！」及「Love you 真男神 真男人」等等。"},{"pid":"4facdef25f831b0b89b64abd0ecaa76fe008f223","tid":1511116,"uid":10949,"like":8,"dislike":55,"score":-47,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"咁係佢本身冇市場價值，所以先可以講真話姐"},{"pid":"7f19df0df25453d0a3da02ba1680eb23aa27dc95","tid":1511116,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4facdef25f831b0b89b64abd0ecaa76fe008f223","tid":1511116,"uid":10949,"like":8,"dislike":55,"score":-47,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"咁係佢本身冇市場價值，所以先可以講真話姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b380ad28636b1c82a2320acef15e4f0e5c3827a","tid":1511116,"uid":149496,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4facdef25f831b0b89b64abd0ecaa76fe008f223","tid":1511116,"uid":10949,"like":8,"dislike":55,"score":-47,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"咁係佢本身冇市場價值，所以先可以講真話姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"有啲本來冇市場價值嘅諗住奶完共會有水喉射住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8491f0ba360664c79c66435ff7bfe049375949","tid":1511116,"uid":23931,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9b380ad28636b1c82a2320acef15e4f0e5c3827a","tid":1511116,"uid":149496,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4facdef25f831b0b89b64abd0ecaa76fe008f223","tid":1511116,"uid":10949,"like":8,"dislike":55,"score":-47,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"咁係佢本身冇市場價值，所以先可以講真話姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"有啲本來冇市場價值嘅諗住奶完共會有水喉射住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re